tool_description:
Cricket live score service at CricketApi allows you to follow real time cricket results, standings and fixtures. Live matches from cricket leagues has ball by ball coverage for every inning and detailed tables for fall of the wicket and partnership.
For increased rates and more sports, please look at: https://rapidapi.com/fluis.lacasse/api/allsportsapi2/
name: CricketAPI2
title: CricketAPI2

api_list.name: Search
api_list.description: Search cricket players, teams, and tournaments using a search term.

required_parameters.name: term
required_parameters.description: The search term to find cricket-related entities.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com/api/cricket/search/kabul"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

import requests

url = "https://cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com/api/cricket/search/{term}"

            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

print(response.json())

api_list.name: MatchH2HDuel
api_list.description: Get head-to-head duel information for a specific cricket match.

required_parameters.name: id
required_parameters.description: The ID of the cricket match for which you want to get head-to-head duel information.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com/api/cricket/match/10534787/duel"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
api_list.convert_code:
import requests

url = "https://cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com/api/cricket/match/{id}/duel"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
